{% set description %}
  A fieldset is for grouping one or many form inputs.
{% endset %}

{% set notes %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>All inputs must be wrapped with a fieldset using <code>form-fieldset.twig</code>. Multiple fieldsets can be used if it is necessary to group certain form inputs.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Each fieldset must have a legend. Use <code>legendTitle</code> to set the legend text; use <code>legendSize</code> to set the legend text size.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>To visually hide a legend, use <code>legendAttributes</code> to add the class <code>u-bolt-visuallyhidden</code>. This will still allow screen readers to access the legend.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Set helper text for a fieldset via the <code>descriptionText</code> prop.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Set error messages for a fieldset via the <code>errors</code> prop.</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endset %}

